sokochan

Class SokochanGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • sokochan.SokochanGrid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TileGridObject>

    public final class SokochanGrid
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<TileGridObject>
    This class wraps a two dimensional array of Tiles (that will be implemented as an array of arrays in Java, because of the lack of thereof) and provides a series of methods to retrieve GridObjects and Tiles placed in a position. The class implements Iterable, in order to simplify the reading of all the objects, for such purpose it contains an inner class called GridIterator. Note: in the SokochanGrid are placed only Tiles, Crates and WarehouseKeeper are paced inside the Tile. Created by Vittorio on 05-Oct-16.
